attributionInfo.brokerName: WNC Real Estate at Lake James

data.description: Single level living with room for your entire family! The expansive 3070 sq. ft main house boasts 4 bedrooms and 2.5 baths. The kitchen has rare, wormy chestnut cabinets and plenty of space for those that love to cook. The beautiful hardwood floors are made of ash wood. The back patio leads to a separate 1632 sq.ft guest house with 2 bedrooms and 2 full baths. The guest house would be ideal for a mother-in-law suite or rental/Airbnb for income generation. Directly across from the guest house is a 2352 sq.ft 2-story garage with 3 bays. The second floor of the garage is studded for future finish, ready and waiting for your vision to come to life! With over 20 acres, this would make a great equestrian/farm property and much of the back is cleared pastureland. The tractor barn in the back is there to store all of your heavy equipment. At one time, there was a pool on the property - while the pool is no longer there, the 656 sq.ft pool house remains and has a bathroom. Don't miss this one!
